        <h1>Lala Lajpat Rai Study Center..</h1>
          <img class="imgr borderedbox" src="images1/lala%20lajpat%20rai.png" alt="">
 
        <p><font color="black">In Hindu College the UGC  has established a Lala Lajpat Rai studies centre.Presently it is the only centre  in India,working  on the ideas and thoughts of Lala Lajpat Rai under the scheme of Epoch Marking Social Thinkers of India.Dr.Arun Mehra,Head,Political Science  Department is its director.The objective of the centre is to acquaint the students with revutionary path breaking thoughts and actions of this great social thinker and leader who has left lasting impact not only inIndia but in the whole world.UGC grant is being utilized to set up library-cum-reading room about Lala Lajpat Rai,to conduct research work on varied aspects of Lala Lajpat Rai and to organize seminars,workshops,lectures and short cources.The centre also provides research facilities regarding thoughts and works of Lala Lajpat Rai.</font> </p>
        <p><font color="black">The centre organized a national seminar on “LALA LAJPAT RAI: A visionary Par-Excellence socio-Economics and political concerns”and also organized a portrait-making workshop on Lala Lajpat Rai.Eminent scholars namely Dr.Rajneesh Arora,vice chancellor,PTU,Dr.Swatantra kumar,vice chancellor,Gurukal university,Haridwar,Dr.Inderjeet Singh,Registrar,GNDU ,Prof.Satish Mittal,Prof H.D Bedi,Prof.Hasrish C.Sharma and many other scholars visited the college and gave their presentations about the varied aspects of Lala Lajpat Rai.Arun Mehra also published a book entitled “Lala Lajpat Rai ;visionary par Excellence.</font> </p>
